high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the side of the round table closest to the counter.
Pick up the metal fork off of the round table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to where the metal frying pan is on the counter.
Place the metal fork into the frying pan handle down.
Pick up the frying pa with the metal fork in it.
Turn left and walk around the counter back over to the round table.
Place the frying pan with the fork in it onto the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a fork in it on a round table.

high_descs: Go forward, then turn right to go to the round table.
Pick up the fork from the center of the table.
Turn left, then go forward, then turn left to go around the kitchen counter.
Put the fork on the pan, on the counter and to the right of the potato.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Go back to the table, on the other side of the counter.
Place the pan on the table, to the left of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork on it on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the end of the left counter, hang a right to the wall and turn left to face the white table.
Pick up the fork to the left of the potato in the middle of the table.
Head left to the end of the table, turn left, walk to the counter top on your left, and turn left to face the angular counter top with the black pan.
Put the fork inside the black pan on the counter top.
Pick up the black pan with the fork inside from the counter top.
Turn left, walk towards the fridge, hang a right past the angular counter, head right to the wall, and turn left to reach the white table.
Place the pan with the fork to the left of the knife on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a black pan with a fork on the table.

high_descs: Cross the room, hang a left at the end of the counter, head towards the wall and turn left to face the white table.
Pick up the silver fork to the left of the potato in the middle of the table.
Turn left, hang a left at the end of the table, cross the room, hang a left to reach the counter top, and turn left to face the counter sitting at an angle.
Put the fork inside the black pan on top of the counter.
Pick up the pan with a fork inside of it from the counter top.
Turn left, head across the room, hang a right at the white table to the wall and turn left to face the table.
Place the pan with the fork to the left of the knife on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a fork on a table.

high_descs: Move toward the wall, turn right move to the table, turn left.
Pick up the fork by the potato.
Turn around, turn left and walk to the counter, turn left.
Put the fork in the fry pan.
Pick up the fry pan from the counter.
Turn left, turn right, walk to the table, turn right
Put the fry pan on the left side of the table next.
anns.task_desc: Get the fork, put in the fry pan, put the fry pan on the table.
